---
---
<section id="about">
    <div class="wrap">
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-visual" data-reveal="left">
                <div class="about-main-card">
                    <span class="big-num">10+</span>
                    <h3>Years Moving South India's Families Forward</h3>
                    <p>From our home in Nellore to 75 cities across 5 states.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-stat-cards">
                    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">5K+</div><div class="stat-lbl">Happy Moves</div></div>
                    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">75</div><div class="stat-lbl">Cities</div></div>
                    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">4.9★</div><div class="stat-lbl">Rating</div></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="about-content" data-reveal="right">
                <span class="t-sm">About PackersHub</span>
                <h2 class="t-h2" style="margin:14px 0 20px">We Don't Just Move <em>Boxes</em>. We Move <span class="t-accent">Lives.</span></h2>
                <p class="t-body" style="margin-bottom:18px">PackersHub was born in Nellore in 2014 from a simple conviction: relocation should be stress-free. Not the panicked, broken-item, where-is-my-truck experience that too many families endure. A planned, professional, respectful process — from the first call to the last box placed in your new home.</p>
                <p class="t-body" style="margin-bottom:36px">Ten years on, we are South India's most trusted relocation network — 75 cities, 5 states, 5,000+ families served, and a team of 100+ professionals who treat your belongings as they would their own. Every truck we own. Every crew member we trained. Every move we personally guarantee.</p>
                <div class="about-features">
                    <div class="about-feat"><div class="about-feat-icon">🏆</div><div class="about-feat-title">Decade of Excellence</div><div class="about-feat-desc">10+ years, zero compromises on quality</div></div>
                    <div class="about-feat"><div class="about-feat-icon">🌏</div><div class="about-feat-title">Pan South India</div><div class="about-feat-desc">5 states, 75 cities, one team</div></div>
                    <div class="about-feat"><div class="about-feat-icon">🔒</div><div class="about-feat-title">Own Fleet</div><div class="about-feat-desc">No sub-contracting. Ever.</div></div>
                    <div class="about-feat"><div class="about-feat-icon">💬</div><div class="about-feat-title">Telugu Support</div><div class="about-feat-desc">24/7 in your language</div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="about-actions">
                    <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Free Quote</a>
                    <a href="tel:+917730912913" class="btn btn-outline">📞 +91 77309 12913</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 100px; align-items: center; }
    .about-visual { position: relative; }
    .about-main-card {
        background: var(--c-brand); border-radius: 32px;
        padding: 52px; color: #fff; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
        aspect-ratio: 4/3;
        display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end;
    }
    .about-main-card::before {
        content: '📦'; font-size: 140px; opacity: .08;
        position: absolute; top: -20px; right: -20px;
        transform: rotate(15deg); line-height: 1;
    }
    .about-main-card .big-num {
        font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: 80px; font-weight: 900;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,.12); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 8px;
        display: block;
    }
    .about-main-card h3 { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; z-index:1; position:relative; }
    .about-main-card p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.65); font-size: 15px; z-index:1; position:relative; }
    
    .about-stat-cards { position: absolute; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; right: -28px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); }
    .stat-card {
        background: var(--c-surface); border-radius: var(--r-md); padding: 16px 20px;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
        min-width: 140px;
    }
    .stat-num { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: 30px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--c-accent); line-height: 1; }
    .stat-lbl { font-size: 12px; color: var(--c-muted); font-weight: 600; margin-top: 3px; }
    
    .about-features { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-top: 36px; }
    .about-feat {
        background: var(--c-surface); border-radius: var(--r-md); padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
        transition: border-color var(--dur-base), transform var(--dur-base) var(--ease-spring);
    }
    .about-feat:hover { border-color: var(--c-brand); transform: translateY(-3px); }
    .about-feat-icon { font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .about-feat-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .about-feat-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--c-muted); line-height: 1.55; }
    
    .about-actions { display: flex; gap: 14px; margin-top: 32px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    @media(max-width:1100px) {
        .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 60px; }
        .about-stat-cards { position: relative; right: auto; top: auto; transform: none; flex-direction: row; }
    }
    @media(max-width:720px) {
        .about-features { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
</style>
